This script testing into VM environment, please update the inventory_file
ansible version 2.0 or later 

ansible-playbook -i inventory_file --become playbook.yml
or for specific group from inventory 
ansible-playbook -i inventory_file -l --become linux_hosts playbook.yml


PermitRootLogin no: Security Best Practices 
AllowUsers : Keep the security one step narrow. Server might have some additionuser system user, this will specific user to connect

Port 2222: This line changes the default SSH port to 2222, Security Best Practices
PermitEmptyPasswords no: Security Best practices , improving security 
